|colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||33||23\n|-\n|rowspan=\"3\"|[[Inter Milan]]\n|[[1998\u201399_Inter_Milan_season|1998\u201399]]\n|rowspan=\"2\"|Serie A\n||23||5||6{{refn|group=lower-alpha|name=intbol|Includes two appearances and one goal in the two-legged [[1998\u201399 Coppa Italia]] third-place tiebreaker round against [[Bologna F.C. 1909|Bologna]] to qualify for the [[1999\u20132000 UEFA Cup]].<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rsssf.com/tablesi/italcup99.html|title=Italy Cup 1998/99|last=Rota|first=Davide|last2=Miladinovich|first2=Misha|publisher=Rec. Sport. Soccer Statistics Foundation|date=17 August 1999|accessdate=15 December 2014}}</ref>}}||1<ref group=lower-alpha name=intbol/>||6<ref group=lower-alpha name=UCL2>All appearances in the [[UEFA Champions League]]; includes two appearances and one goal in the [[1998\u201399 UEFA Champions League#Second qualifying round|second qualifying round]].</ref>||4<ref group=lower-alpha name=UCL2/>||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||35||10\n|-\n|[[1999\u20132000_Inter_Milan_season|1999\u20132000]]\n||19<ref group=lower-alpha name=intpar>Includes appearance and two goals in the [[1999\u20132000 Serie A]] fourth-place tiebreaker match against [[Parma F.C.|Parma]] to qualify for the [[2000\u201301 UEFA Champions League]].</ref>||6<ref group=lower-alpha name=intpar/>||5||1||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||24||7\n|-\n!colspan=\"2\"|Total\n!42||11||11||2||6||4||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||59||17\n|-\n|rowspan=\"5\"|[[Brescia Calcio|Brescia]]\n|[[2000\u201301 Serie A|2000\u201301]]\n|rowspan=\"4\"|Serie A\n||25||10||3||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||28||10\n|-\n|[[2001\u201302_Brescia_Calcio_season|2001\u201302]]\n||12||11||1||0||2<ref group=lower-alpha name=UIC>All appearances in the [[UEFA Intertoto Cup]].</ref>||1||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||15||12\n|-\n|[[2002\u201303_Brescia_Calcio_season|2002\u201303]]\n||32||12||0||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||32||12\n|-\n|[[2003\u201304_Brescia_Calcio_season|2003\u201304]]\n||26|